1. From the Life in the Roller Coster Data
2. Convert this data into a pivot table and find the overall average speed of all rides that satisfy the following criteria:
1.The Type is Steel
2.The Design is Sit Down
3.The Amusement Park has the word adventure somewhere in the title
4. Year Wise Roller Coster wise Average Speed (Show in a trend Line )
5. Type and Design wise Average Speed. All this above analysis should be visualize in the charts. Finally the Sheet should be saved as Holiday Pivot.
